OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe National Trust has announced the
OL,8,Fwinner of its competition to turn the
OL,9,Fwood of the illegally-felled Sycamore
OL,10,FGap tree into a piece of artwork.
OL,12,FSix artists were shortlisted for the
OL,13,Fcommission, which aims to shape the
OL,14,Ftree's next chapter by using half of
OL,15,Fits timber.
OL,17,FHelix Arts and George King Architects
OL,18,Fwon the contest after a national
OL,19,Fpublic vote and final decision by an
OL,20,Fexpert judging panel, the National
OL,21,FTrust said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe arts charity and architects
OL,8,Fstudio, based in North Shields near
OL,9,FNewcastle and London respectively,
OL,10,Fcollaborated on an idea called "The
OL,11,FPeople's Tree".
OL,13,FThe proposal combines public
OL,14,Fparticipation, sound, architecture and
OL,15,Fstorytelling to respond to the loss of
OL,16,Fthe world-famous tree.
OL,26,@rD@`OUsD@NO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FIt comes after Daniel Graham and Adam
OL,8,FCarruthers, from Cumbria, travelled to
OL,9,FHadrian's Wall in Northumberland
OL,10,Fduring Storm Agnes in 2023 to cut it
OL,11,Fdown.
OL,13,FThe felling sparked national outrage
OL,14,Fand an outpouring of grief for the
OL,15,Fwidely-loved landmark, which is
OL,16,Fthought to have been planted in the
OL,17,Flate 1880s.
OL,19,FThe National Trust said the winning
OL,20,Fproposal scored highest across the
OL,21,Fpublic vote and the judges.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FRather than centring on a single
OL,8,Fmemorial, the artwork will involve a
OL,9,FUK-wide programme where members of the
OL,10,Fpublic are invited to record
OL,11,Freflections on their own relationships
OL,12,Fwith trees and nature.
OL,14,FAlongside these sound and spoken word
OL,15,Frecordings, the artists will create a
OL,16,Fdigital soundtrack by scanning the
OL,17,Ftree's rings.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe final compilation of stories and
OL,8,Faudio will then be presented through a
OL,9,Fseries of exhibitions and workshops
OL,10,Fheld to the north, south, east and
OL,11,Fwest of Sycamore Gap.
OL,13,FSections of some of the seasoned wood
OL,14,Fwill also be used to co-create
OL,15,Fartworks with communities and local
OL,16,Fartists.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FAfter these exhibitions and workshops,
OL,8,Fthe project will culminate in a "sound
OL,9,Fsculpture" ` an artwork that includes
OL,10,Fsome of its wood as well as the
OL,11,Farchive of stories and nature sounds,
OL,12,Fwhich will be placed in an accessible
OL,13,Flocation along Hadrian's Wall.
OL,15,FCheryl Gavin, director at Helix Arts,
OL,16,Fsaid: "To be chosen by both the public
OL,17,Fand the judging panel feels phenomenal.
OL,26,@pD@aOUqD@JO]xD@GOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"This project comes from a belief that
OL,8,Fthe legacy of the Sycamore Gap tree
OL,9,Flives not only in its wood, but in the
OL,10,Frelationships, memories and moments of
OL,11,Fconnection it sparked."
OL,13,FGeorge King, from George King
OL,14,FArchitects, said: "It is a real honour
OL,15,Fto be entrusted with responding to a
OL,16,Fplace that means so much to so many
OL,17,Fpeople.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@WO]vD@SOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"The tree as it was can never be
OL,8,Freplaced, but what we can do is create
OL,9,Fa place for reflection and
OL,10,Fconnections."
OL,12,FAnnie Reilly, public engagement
OL,13,Fdirector at the National Trust and
OL,14,Fchairwoman of the judging panel, said:
OL,15,F"What stood out about this proposal
OL,16,Fwas how it puts a real conversation
OL,17,Fbetween people and the tree at its
OL,18,Fheart.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@MO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"It doesn't try to give one answer to
OL,8,Floss. Instead, it invites people to
OL,9,Flisten, reflect and reconnect ` with
OL,10,Fnature and with each other."
OL,12,FThe project will now move into a
OL,13,Fdevelopment phase, with Helix Arts and
OL,14,FGeorge King Architects working closely
OL,15,Fwith the National Trust, local
OL,16,Fpartners and communities along
OL,17,FHadrian's Wall.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@\O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe public's participation in the
OL,8,Fproject is expected to start from this
OL,9,Fsummer, with the completed work set to
OL,10,Fbe realised by September 2027.
OL,12,FThe initiative comes as part of a
OL,13,Fwider public engagement programme
OL,14,Fresponding to the tree's felling,
OL,15,Fsupported by Northumberland National
OL,16,FPark Authority (NNPA), Historic
OL,17,FEngland, the Hadrian's Wall
OL,18,FPartnership and the National Trust.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FSo far, the main section of the tree's
OL,8,Ftrunk has been installed at the
OL,9,Fgateway to Northumberland National
OL,10,FPark, where the tree once stood.
OL,12,FHeartwood prints from a cross-section
OL,13,Fof the trunk created by printmaker
OL,14,FShona Branigan are now on display at
OL,15,FSeaton Delaval Hall in Northumberland.
OL,17,FUK communities were invited to apply
OL,18,Ffor one of the 49 saplings grown from
OL,19,Fseeds rescued from the original tree,
OL,20,Fwhich have now been planted across the
OL,21,Fcountry.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1779872680
OL,3,CArtist to create work from Sycamore
OL,4,CGap tree wood after contest winner
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe National Trust also confirmed on
OL,8,FSaturday that, for the third
OL,9,Fconsecutive year, several shoots are
OL,10,Fregrowing from the stump, giving
OL,11,Ffurther confidence that one day a new
OL,12,Ftree will grow in the Gap.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/12
